---
// Hero セクション — ファーストビュー
---

<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-white to-primary-50 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- 背景デコレーション -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-primary-100 opacity-30 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -left-40 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-accent-100 opacity-20 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-20 pb-16 lg:pt-28 lg:pb-24">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- コピー -->
      <div>
        <!-- バッジ -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 text-xs font-semibold mb-5">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" />
          </svg>
          IT経営力大賞2009 経済産業大臣賞 受賞
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-5">
          中小製造業の<br class="sm:hidden" />生産管理を、<br />
          <span class="text-primary-600">クラウドで。</span><br class="sm:hidden" />シンプルに。
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          受注から出荷、生産計画まで。必要な機能を選べる、<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          サーバー不要のクラウド型生産管理システムです。<br class="hidden sm:block" />
          導入実績 15社以上。
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
          <a
            href="/contact/"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl bg-primary-600 text-white font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors shadow-md shadow-primary-200"
          >
            資料請求・お問い合わせ
            <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="/pricing/"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3.5 rounded-xl border-2 border-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-semibold text-sm hover:border-primary-300 hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors"
          >
            料金を見る
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- 信頼指標 -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-5 mt-8 text-sm text-slate-500">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            導入実績 15社以上
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            社内サーバー不要
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            2007年から稼働実績
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 製品イメージ（スクリーンショット） -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200 border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100">
          <!-- ブラウザ風ヘッダー -->
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 px-4 py-3 bg-slate-800">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-400"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-400"></div>
            <div class="ml-3 flex-1 bg-slate-700 rounded text-xs text-slate-400 px-3 py-1 text-center">
              app.tfgdata.jp
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- スクリーンショット or プレースホルダー -->
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-primary-900 flex items-center justify-center">
            <img
              src="/images/screenshots/dashboard.png"
              alt="PT-SaaS ダッシュボード画面"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
              onerror="this.parentElement.innerHTML='<div class=\'flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full h-full text-white opacity-60 gap-3\'><svg class=\'w-12 h-12\' fill=\'none\' stroke=\'currentColor\' viewBox=\'0 0 24 24\'><path stroke-linecap=\'round\' stroke-linejoin=\'round\' stroke-width=\'1\' d=\'M9 17V7m0 10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10V7m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2a2 2 0 00-2 2\' /></svg><span class=\'text-sm font-medium\'>スクリーンショット準備中</span></div>'"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- フローティングバッジ -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-3 border border-slate-100">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-800">EDI受信完了</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">受注データを自動取込</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
